environmentalDataLogging.entities

Class Device

  • java.lang.Object
    • environmentalDataLogging.entities.BaseEntity
      • environmentalDataLogging.entities.Device

  • @Entity
public class Device
extends BaseEntity
    The Device entity class is the link to the device table in the EnviroDB database. A Device is used by the Environmental Technologies lab to create samples.
